edu.xtec.jclic.edit

Class EditorAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.AbstractAction
      • edu.xtec.jclic.edit.EditorAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionListener, Serializable, Cloneable, EventListener, Action

    public abstract class EditorAction
extends AbstractAction
    This abstract class provides a base to create Action objects related to Editors. Derived classes must implement only the doAction method, executing the required operations on the supplied Editor.
    Version:
    13.08.28
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
